Package net.sourceforge.plantuml.argon2

package net.sourceforge.plantuml.argon2
Provides classes used to manage the Password-Hashing Function nammed Argon2.

The code is taken from:

  • Andreas1327250/Argon2-java
  • Alphazero/Blake2b/

Ref.:

  • P-H-C/PHC-winner-argon2
  • Password Hashing Competition (PHC)
